<div id="pfa" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="a"><div class="pc pca w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w0 h0" alt="" src="bga.png"/><div class="t m7 x16 h2f y8e ff47 fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">Horses are beautiful animals </span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y8f ff47 fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">with strong muscles.  A horse </span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y90 ff47 fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">can easily carry a person on </span><span class="ws0"><span class="fc2 sc0"> </span></span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y91 ff47 fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">its back.</span></div><div class="t m7 x2e h2e y92 ff48 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws2"><span class="fc2 sc0">All About Horses</span></div><div class="t m7 x33 h2d y55 ff49 fs1b fc1 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc2 sc0">8</span></div><div class="c x20 y0 w9 h0"><div class="t m7 x16 h2f y93 ff4a fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">Horses are fast, too.  They </span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y94 ff4a fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">are one of the fastest animals in </span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y95 ff4a fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">the world.  People like to watch </span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y96 ff4a fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">horse races and guess which </span></div><div class="t m7 x22 h2f y97 ff4a fs20 fc1 sc0 ls0 ws4"><span class="fc2 sc0">horse will run the fastest.</span></div><div class="t m7 x4a h35 y98 ff4b fs1b fc1 sc0 ls0 ws5"><span class="fc2 sc0">A horse’s powerful legs help </span></div><div class="t m7 x4a h35 y99 ff4b fs1b fc1 sc0 ls0 ws5"><span class="fc2 sc0">the animal run far and jump </span></div><div class="t m7 x4a h35 y9a ff4b fs1b fc1 sc0 ls0 ws5"><span class="fc2 sc0">high.  Some horses can run </span></div><div class="t m7 x4a h35 y9b ff4b fs1b fc1 sc0 ls0 ws5"><span class="fc2 sc0">more than 50 miles per hour!</span></div><div class="t m7 x34 h2d y55 ff4c fs1b fc1 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc2 sc0">9</span></div></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
